rComments: Excellent professor and class. Highly recommended for those who appreciate instruction and learning that involves critical analysis and engagement in a collaborative classroom environment.

This guy is a really nice guy.  I took this class for Summer Session I and the bulk of what we did was watch movies and eat food we brought in.  There were only a couple take-home exams in essay form and one formal paper.  Take this class.  You won't regret it.
